# Title: Suspicious Creation with Colorcpl
# Author: frack113
# Date: 2022-01-21
# Level: high
# Description: Once executed, colorcpl.exe will copy the arbitrary file to c:\windows\system32\spool\drivers\color\
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1564
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/file/file_event/file_event_win_susp_colorcpl.yml

Image="*\\colorcpl.exe" NOT (TargetFilename IN ("*.icm", "*.gmmp", "*.cdmp", "*.camp"))